posting_body: ['136 Washington Street managed by Cornerstone Apartments', 'Bedrooms:', '1', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Square Ft.:', '445', 'Price:', '$1205/mo.', 'Southern walkways and entries soak up the sun throughout the year on Washington Street.', 'Updated, comfortable apartments in central Denver are close to the Cherry Creek bike trail, which acts like a subway to all the best parts of town, just hop on the trail and zip downtown or for a more extensive ride outside of the city.', 'Features:', 'On-Site Laundry', 'Recycling', 'Smoke-Free Building', 'Storage', 'A/C', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Shared Community WiFi', 'Controlled Entry', 'Reserved Parking', 'Courtyard', 'Contact us:', 'To schedule a showing please contact our leasing team at', 'To apply NOW please visit <URL>', 'Nearby Neighborhoods:', "University of Denver, Sloan's Lake, Cheesman Park, Downtown, Highlands, City Park, Jefferson Park, RiNo, Hale, Baker, West Wash Park, LoHi, Five Points, Capitol Hill, Platt Park, Uptown, Congress Park", 'Availability and pricing are subject to change.']
